name: Flamin' Hot Cheetos Nike Elite Socks
description:
Iconic Socks* Custom Nike Elite Socks are not sold in stores anywhere...These were created exclusively by Iconic Socks in Arizona. The Printing Process we use permanently dyes the socks and they feel no different than an elite that has not been dyed. 

PLEASE ALLOW 3-5 DAYS FOR ORDER PROCESSING BECAUSE OF THE HIGH DEMAND!!! WE CUSTOM MAKE EACH PAIR ON DEMAND. 

A TRACKING NUMBER WILL BE GIVEN ONCE ORDER IS SHIPPED, WE SHIP USING USPS FIRST CLASS MAIL.

All socks pre-stretched

SIZING CHART

MEN'S:
S	 3Y-5Y	
M	 6-8	
L	 8-12	
XL 12-15

WOMENS:
S	 4-6
M	 6-10
L	 10-13
XL	 N/A

PRODUCT SPECIFICATION:
• Dri-fit fabric that pulls away sweat to help keep you cool and comfortable 
• Reinforced heel and toe for enhanced durability 
• Left/Right specific design for a better fit 
• Supportive fit with arch compression 
• Stripes up the back

PLEASE READ: These are AUTHENTIC Custom Nike Elite Basketball Crew Socks, with designs & colors inspired by basketball players and athletic Shoes. All packaging is original. Each sock ordered will be different as no two socks are alike due to our process to create the sock. Rarely some areas of the socks have 1 to 2 small white imperfections because of the creating process. Please look at images of socks what is represented in images is what you will get.


*These are NOT approved/authenticated by Nike

Nike logo and Nike name are registered trademarks of Nike, Inc. 
This is an independent shop that is not affiliated with Nike, Inc.


Product Info
The Nike Elite Basketball Crew Sock features Midfoot Compression Fit that helps keep socks and cushioning in place. Footstrike cushioning. Clearly defined pattern is closely aligned to pressure patterns on the feet. Dri-FIT® fabric wicks away moisture to help keep feet dry and cool. Anatomical left and right, superior fit and cushioning. Sold as single pair. 62% polyester/21% nylon/15% cotton/2% spandex.
